text: Hey participants! If today is your first day, come talk to us (orange lanyards) and we can help you.

Hey guys, I just arrived today. I don't have a group yet, and I don't need to be in one particular. If you need help in listening to your presentation, pitch, visualisation or just want someone to debrief to, let me know. I'm in a grey jumper or red shirt depending on how cold I get. I also can also be a resource for finance and health domains.
